            p Similarly to commercial Linux service providers, Alliance members offer training, coaching, tailoring and consulting to help organizations apply the XSCALE practice pattern languages.
            p The Alliance admits highly experienced Coaches to train Practitioners in XSCALE patterns. Different coaches have different strengths; effective transformation requires a mix of coaches to cover:
