          h3 Practitioner Training
          ul
            li XSCALE Practitioner certification has neither maintenance costs, experience requirements, nor sunset clauses. Practitioner certification simply means competence to practice. Once issued, it never expires.
            li Most Practitioner training is delivered in the course of a <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/fixed-price-agile-transformation-peter-merel/">self-propagating transformation</a>. To open the ecosystem we also conduct public courses, and the table here lists upcoming public sessions.
            li If you're not physically available in any of these locations you can contact any <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/xscale-alliance-seeking-worlds-best-agile-trainers-coaches-merel">XSCALE Steward</a> to arrange remote training. We're keen to involve your existing Agile coaches and trainers in our ecosystem and we're happy to train them in conjunction with Practitioner training sessions.
            li The 1-day XAC course is $1,099<sup>*</sup>. 2-day Practitioner courses are $2,399 each<sup>*</sup>. Contact your friendly neighborhood <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/pulse/xscale-alliance-seeking-worlds-best-agile-trainers-coaches-merel/">XSCALE Steward</a> to ask about discounts and promotions available in your region.
